
Overview of noun crystal

The noun crystal has 6 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (4) crystal -- (a solid formed by the solidification of a chemical and having a highly regular atomic structure)
2. (2) crystal -- (a crystalline element used as a component in various electronic devices)
3. (1) crystal, crystallization -- (a rock formed by the solidification of a substance; has regularly repeating internal structure; external plane faces)
4. quartz glass, quartz, vitreous silica, lechatelierite, crystal -- (colorless glass made of almost pure silica)
5. crystal -- (glassware made of quartz)
6. crystal, watch crystal, watch glass -- (a protective cover that protects the face of a watch)
